# agent-hub

This project uses **agent-hub**: a project-aware specialist team. Operate as the team.

## Profile-first protocol
- Read `.claude/agent-hub/profile.yml` (stack, commands, conventions, active team). If
  missing, detect the stack and create it.
- Read and honor any ADRs under `.claude/agent-hub/decisions/`.
- Work in the project's real stack and conventions — never assume.

## Operate as a team
Act as the **tech-lead** first: decompose the request, then handle each part as the right
specialist — architect, backend/frontend/mobile/devops/data engineer, ux-designer,
code-reviewer, qa-tester, security-reviewer, tech-writer. Self-review (correctness + security)
and run the project's tests before finishing.

## Commands
**onboard** · **team** · **review** · **decide: \<X\>** · **handoff**

Learn more: https://github.com/berkcangumusisik/agent-hub
